Requirements:

You must add:
3 firewalls
1 SSL certificate to serve www.foobar.com over HTTPS
3 monitoring clients (data collector for Sumologic or other monitoring services)

Visual presentation
https://imgur.com/a/RYppWn2

For every additional element, why you are adding it

What are firewalls for
Are used to prevent unauthorized access into or out of a computer.It protect the user and the private network user.

Why is the traffic served over HTTPS
With a HTTPS connection, all communications are securely encrypted. This means that even if somebody managed to break into the connection, they would not be able decrypt any of the data which passes between you and the website.

What monitoring is used for
The Monitoring allows results, processes and experiences to be documented and used as a basis to steer decision-making and learning processes.

How the monitoring tool is collecting data
THey collect data about systems and making sure they are not beind overloaded and are working as expected.

Explain what to do if you want to monitor your web server QPS
they observing the systems and providing a number of key metrics.
